originalText.text: Dr. Kulick is an excellent Doctor.  He is very knowledgeable about medications, and other treatments for depression, such as TMS, and about the work and research of other doctors in the field.  He is a good listener. Also, I have to say that last year, during the Christmas Holiday period, Dr. Kulick was the only psychiatrist I know who had office hours and was seeing patients.  I respect him very much.

originalText.text:
I am a patient of Dr. Kulick and I'm sad to say in
January, due to insurance he will not be be my Dr.  He was the first Dr. That explained in detail
Why and how medication is needed.  I feel so comfortable with him. I will do everything in my power not to lose him as my Dr. Just thinking about it makes me sad. I always loved his feedback. Hopefully 2017 he will remain my Dr
